tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE vpn_performance_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date TIMESTAMP,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    download_speed INT,
    upload_speed INT
)

CREATE TABLE vpn_performance (
    date DATE,
    user_id INT,
    server_name VARCHAR,
    download_speed INT,
    upload_speed INT
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_usage (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id int,
    vpn_server_id int,
    start_time timestamp,
    end_time timestamp
);

CREATE TABLE vpn_usage (
    usage_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    connection_id UUID NOT NULL,
    usage_date DATE,
    data_transferred INTEGER
);
